  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3452040/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.poster.avif?t=1740047714\" width=600 height=82 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3452040/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.webm?t=1740047714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3452040/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.mp4?t=1740047714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3452040/extras/7932adb8d13059561e9526e3dda21cae.poster.avif?t=1740047714\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3452040/extras/7932adb8d13059561e9526e3dda21cae.webm?t=1740047714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3452040/extras/7932adb8d13059561e9526e3dda21cae.mp4?t=1740047714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >HISTORY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are Nina, a young top model who was kidnapped by an evil pharmaceutical company called MEDIO.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >MEDIO kidnapped up to 100 street workers with the complicity of Mayor James Hugh. MEDIO wants to experiment with a new cream that can restore youth to its customers, they call it Venus cream. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The lead scientist is Alice RAUP and she had no pity for the young street workers used as guinea pigs for the NovoVenus program.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >They realized at some point that most of the experiment subjects had developed very worrying symptoms.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The evacuation protocol was applied against a potential loss of control of the building linked to the NovoVenus program.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3452040/extras/c6c2986b258d92afdfd916eef9c13df1.poster.avif?t=1740047714\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3452040/extras/c6c2986b258d92afdfd916eef9c13df1.webm?t=1740047714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3452040/extras/c6c2986b258d92afdfd916eef9c13df1.mp4?t=1740047714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GAME FEATURE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Exploration of the floors</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hidden objects to find to progress in the game</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Obstacles or doors requiring you to crouch </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Using a Pistol or Assault Rifle for 3rd Person Shooting</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dodging system similar to Resident Evil 3 remake.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customizing the main character's body.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Main character with attractive appearance</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Basic and original inventory system.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CHALLENGE/CHALLENGE mode in which you must reach an evacuation point without being killed by zombies. It's time to go wild!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The game will be available on February 20, 2025 at a very attractive price!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3452040/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.poster.avif?t=1740047714\" width=600 height=82 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3452040/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.webm?t=1740047714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3452040/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.mp4?t=1740047714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3452040/extras/7932adb8d13059561e9526e3dda21cae.poster.avif?t=1740047714\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3452040/extras/7932adb8d13059561e9526e3dda21cae.webm?t=1740047714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3452040/extras/7932adb8d13059561e9526e3dda21cae.mp4?t=1740047714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >HISTORY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are Nina, a young top model who was kidnapped by an evil pharmaceutical company called MEDIO.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >MEDIO kidnapped up to 100 street workers with the complicity of Mayor James Hugh. MEDIO wants to experiment with a new cream that can restore youth to its customers, they call it Venus cream. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The lead scientist is Alice RAUP and she had no pity for the young street workers used as guinea pigs for the NovoVenus program.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >They realized at some point that most of the experiment subjects had developed very worrying symptoms.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The evacuation protocol was applied against a potential loss of control of the building linked to the NovoVenus program.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3452040/extras/c6c2986b258d92afdfd916eef9c13df1.poster.avif?t=1740047714\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3452040/extras/c6c2986b258d92afdfd916eef9c13df1.webm?t=1740047714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3452040/extras/c6c2986b258d92afdfd916eef9c13df1.mp4?t=1740047714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GAME FEATURE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Exploration of the floors</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hidden objects to find to progress in the game</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Obstacles or doors requiring you to crouch </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Using a Pistol or Assault Rifle for 3rd Person Shooting</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dodging system similar to Resident Evil 3 remake.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customizing the main character's body.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Main character with attractive appearance</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Basic and original inventory system.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CHALLENGE/CHALLENGE mode in which you must reach an evacuation point without being killed by zombies. It's time to go wild!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The game will be available on February 20, 2025 at a very attractive price!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
